### LISTAR PERFILES
GET {{baseUrl}}/profiles
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### OBTENER PERFIL POR ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/profiles/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ACTUALIZAR PERFIL POR ID
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/profiles/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

